## title

### Source (en)

~~~text
Could you use data aggregation to make the data openly available?
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
您是否可以透過資料聚合（Data Aggregation）使資料更加開放可用？
~~~

## text

### Source (en)

~~~text
Aggregated data, where typically at least 15 individuals are in any data point, are considered sufficiently anonymous. This is an alternative way of making data openly available for future research.
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
彙整後的資料（通常每一個資料點至少包含 15 個個體）被視為具有足夠的匿名性。這也是一種能公開資料給未來研究的替代作法。
~~~
